# SNBB Atlas Pack

A BIDS-compatible parcellation atlas repository for the Strauss Neuroplasticity Brain Bank (SNBB), providing atlases not shipped with QSIRecon/PennLINC.

Atlases included: TianS1–S4 (Melbourne Subcortex), HCPex, HCPMMP, Schaefer-Tian.

See https://github.com/GalKepler/snbb-atlas-pack for details.
